13:29.909 --> 13:31.508
What?

13:31.545 --> 13:33.310
Fox: Millard, don't.

13:34.514 --> 13:35.613
Stop staring at her.

13:35.615 --> 13:37.582
Mark: I-I wasn't.
I'm not.

13:37.717 --> 13:39.217
Silver fox: Aw!

13:39.352 --> 13:41.986
He was her little boyfriend.

13:42.022 --> 13:44.388
He's still in love.

13:44.457 --> 13:46.391
[kissy noises]

13:46.526 --> 13:47.425
[brothers laugh]

13:47.427 --> 13:49.694
