<i> feels like it can never end...</i>

13:56.135 --> 13:57.435
<i> Until it does.</i>

13:57.570 --> 14:00.138
No...?

14:00.140 --> 14:03.074
[brothers laugh]

14:03.076 --> 14:07.478
[emotional music]

14:07.480 --> 14:08.913
