<i> ♪ when I'm faced</i>
<i> with the knowledge ♪</i>

19:55.662 --> 19:59.830
<i> ♪ that you just</i>
<i> don't love me... ♪</i>

19:59.966 --> 20:02.099
Adult mark:<i> You never know</i>
<i> the value of a moment</i>

20:02.101 --> 20:05.503
<i> Until it becomes a memory.</i>

20:05.505 --> 20:09.039
<i> ♪ or say things</i>
<i> to hurt you... ♪</i>

20:09.108 --> 20:11.641
Adult mark:<i> If only we knew</i>
<i> what ones we would yearn for</i>

20:11.643 --> 20:12.977
<i> When we are older.</i>

20:13.112 --> 20:17.582
<i> Then we could soak them in</i>
<i> before they were gone forever.</i>

20:17.717 --> 20:19.917
<i> Maybe then we would</i>
<i> have fewer regrets.</i>

20:21.187 --> 20:26.190
<i>♪ or raise my hands to you... ♪</i>

20:26.325 --> 20:29.927
<i> ♪ now, come on,</i>
<i> you know me too well. ♪</i>

20:29.929 --> 20:32.997
♪

20:33.132 --> 20:35.733
<i> ♪ how could I hurt you... ♪</i>

20:35.868 --> 20:37.735
Fox: It's over!
Leave me alone.

20:37.804 --> 20:40.104
Millard: Are you kidding?
Wait, wait, wait!

20:40.173 --> 20:41.639
Is this 'cause of
that little geek?

20:41.774 --> 20:43.407
Frig off!

20:44.377 --> 20:47.011
[quietly] oh...
He's dead.

